Title: Flamco Flamcovent smart clean separator 100F
Description: Protecting boilers, pumps and fittings from the damage caused by dirt deposits, the Flamco Flamcovent 100F 4 micron smart clean separator helps to increase comfort and improve yield. Beneficial to older systems or in conversions from open to closed system, this steel-built separator is capable of removing the smallest of microbubbles in addition to the tiniest dirt particles. Offering performance levels 60% better than conventional air and dirt separators, the Flamcovent's flow resistance is reduced to a negligible level.

Title: Spirotech SpiroTrap  SV3-028-CUM3 dirt seperater MB3 28mm Filter
Description: Effectively protecting your water system for a longer working life, the Spirotech SpiroTrap MB3 dirt separator, with 28mm connections, removes magnetic and non-magnetic dirt particles using unique magnetic field booster technology. Ensuring removal of even the smallest magnetite particles, the SpiroTrap maximises system performance for a longer, more efficient life with less risk of costly damage to important components such as your system's pump.
